# app image build context guard (W7-D review MED): the image must be safe to build from
# ANY checkout — never rely on rsync excludes. Secrets stay out (rule 12).
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
orbetra_design
.env
.env.*
# ADR-030: public pk. Mapbox token — the web vite build inside the image reads it
!apps/web/.env
.claude
apps/web/dist
playwright-report
test-results
var
